<i>Cannabis</i> <i>was</i> <i>one</i> <i>of</i> <i>the</i> <i>first
plants</i> <i>to</i> <i>be</i> <i>cultivated</i> <i>by</i> <i>man,</i>

00:28.738 --> 00:30.448
<i>and</i> <i>it</i> <i>didn't</i> <i>take</i> <i>long</i> <i>to
discover</i> <i>that</i> <i>this</i> <i>simple</i> <i>leaf</i>

00:32.074 --> 00:36.203
<i>would be the door we needed
to understand who we really are.</i>

00:37.496 --> 00:40.624
<i>It's a window
into the duality of our lives,</i>

00:42.168 --> 00:44.003
<i>into the duality of our souls.</i>

00:45.880 --> 00:50.134
<i>Behind</i> <i>this</i> <i>simple</i> <i>leaf</i> <i>there's</i> <i>an
