<i>a secret to destroy.</i>

01:02.146 --> 01:03.147
<i>The question is:</i>

01:04.523 --> 01:06.776
<i>Which of these paths
do you want to go down?</i>

01:13.282 --> 01:14.950
And the answer to this...

01:16.660 --> 01:18.704
is hidden in each of our souls.

01:21.290 --> 01:22.708
Within you, Felix.

01:23.959 --> 01:24.877
Within you, Ignacio.

01:27.296 --> 01:28.714
And within you, Mariana.

01:40.059 --> 01:41.185
Here's the cash.

01:42.019 --> 01:43.187
The cash can wait.

01:49.109 --> 01:51.821
You're not buying the seeds
before trying them.

01:54.865 --> 01:56.367
Who's going first?

02:14.176 --> 02:16.136
<i>Felix! Felix, wake up.</i>

02:16.178 --> 02:17.763
Fuck, wake up, Felix!

02:17.805 --> 02:19.473
- Where are we?
- We're in deep shit.

02:19.515 --> 02:20.599
Let's go!

02:21.308 --> 02:23.727
Felix! Felix! Felix!

03:24.955 --> 03:29.877
SIX MONTHS LATER

04:19.009 --> 04:19.551
This is paradise.

04:20.636 --> 04:22.471
And you haven't even
tried it yet.

04:23.222 --> 04:24.098
Smell them.

04:28.519 --> 04:30.980
